# Deploying to Heroku

There are two enironments:
- heroku-dev - https://blogger-cloud-dev.herokuapp.com/
- heroku-prod - https://blogger-cloud.herokuapp.com/

## Deploy to Production

In order to deploy to production run:

git push heroku-prod main

## Deploy to Develop

In order to deploy to develop run:

git push heroku-dev develop:main

# Reading from the databases

### Run in a web app (pgweb):

- prod: heroku config:get DATABASE_URL --remote heroku-prod | xargs pgweb --url
- dev: heroku config:get DATABASE_URL --remote heroku-dev | xargs pgweb --url

### Run in any mac app:

- prod: heroku config:get DATABASE_URL --remote heroku-prod
- prod: heroku config:get DATABASE_URL --remote heroku-dev

In mac app open database with URL -> (output of above)

Enusre SSL is enabled.
